Luca Naso has a PhD in Astrophysics and is passionate about Data Science, Machine Learning, Big Data and Startups. That's why he works as Product Development Manager and Data Scientist at Neodata, and has previously worked as Mentor for TIM #Wcap Accelerator (the largest Italian corporate startup accelerator).

He loves new digital technologies, supports the data-driven approach and believes that a smart use of data can dramatically improve the quality of people's everyday life.

Main competencies:
- Project management, Team management, Agile methodology (Scrum), Product development, R&D;
- Machine Learning, Mathematical modelling, Statistics, Regression, Classification, Clustering, Data mining, Data visualisation, Dashboard design;
- Python, R, Hadoop, Hive, SQL, Parallel computing, Amazon, AWS, Lambda, Microsoft, Excel, Azure, HDInsight, Tableau;
- Analytic skills, Problem-solving, Communication skills, Teaching;
- Startups, Business model development, Lean methodology.

As a scientist:
- Magnetic field in proto neutron-stars, magnetic field in accretion discs, magnetic torques in X-Ray binaries;
- Star-disc interaction in galactic centres;
- Writing parallel codes for solving systems of partial differential equations, running codes on High-Performance Computing architectures. ;1

PhD with 10 years experience data mining in Astrophysics. Published 13 as first author from total > 50 scientific papers in high-impact scientific journals. Mentored 3 student researchers; co-founded research projects.

Strong background in data analysis and data modelling:
- Data mining, pre-processing of data;
- Advanced descriptive analysis and data visualization;
- Methods of mathematical statistics;
- Predictions with machine learning techniques;
- Python, Matlab/Octave, KNIME, MySQL, topcat;1

16+ years FreeBSD/ LINUX Programming experiences/ Web Expert/ Machine Learning/ Data Mining/ Information Retrieval/ Natural Language Processing/ Computational linguistics/ Data Science/ Data Compression/ Data Analytics/ Recommender Systems/ Online Advertising/ Online Reputation Management/ Algorithms/ Applied Mathematics/ Mathematical Statistics experiences.

Specialties: FreeBSD/LINUX, Embeded LINUX, TCP/IP, MySQL, NoSQL, Python/PHP/Perl/C/C++/Swift/Java/Scala/SQL, Magento, High Performance Computing, Machine Learning/Deep Learning/Reinforcement Learning/Data Mining/IR/Natural Language Processing/Computational linguistics/Data Science/Data Compression/Data Analytics/Recommender Systems/Online Advertising/Algorithms/Applied Mathematics/Statistics. 

Experiences to build the high-volume, high-availability, large-scale, distributed, intelligent architecture ( ML/DL/DM/NLP/Web/Mobile/Data Analytics system);

